steg0.tittel: Download and fill in the form

lastOppVedlegg.ingress: You can upload attachments to your case here. You must upload all the attachments before NAV can process the case.
lastOppVedlegg.advarselHovedskjema: UTGÅR!! Du får ikke sendt inn før du har lastet opp ferdig utfylt skjema på forrige side.

liste: Open and fill in the downloaded pdf form.
Save the form on your device after filling it out.
Find and upload the completed form.
You can upload any attachments in the next step.

annet.beskrivelse: Give a descriptive name to the document you wish to upload.

feilmelding.fullforRedigering: Complete and confirm the attachment description
feilmelding.navnForLangt: The attachment description is too long. Max {{maxLength}} characters.

radio.sendesAvAndre: Will be submitted by others (e.g. doctor, employer)

feilmelding.ikkeFerdigOpplastet: Wait until the file has finished uploading

soknad.beskjedOmAvvik: Have you experienced problems submitting attachments? Please upload the attachment again and press Submit.

fortsettSenere.tittel: Are you sure you want to save the form and continue later?
liste: The form will NOT be sent to the case manager in NAV now, but only saved so that you can continue later.
If you want to set today's date as the start date for the application, you must click “Cancel” and select “Send to NAV”.
We create a task at nav.no/minside (my page) with a link to the application.

slett.tittel: Are you sure you want to delete the application?
liste: The application and all documents you have uploaded will be deleted.

sendInnUferdig.tittel: Are you sure you want to send the application now, even though some documents have not been uploaded?
liste: Today's date will be set as the date of receipt of the application.
You have not uploaded all the documents required to process the application.
You must send the missing documents by {{dato}}.
We will create a task to upload the missing documents. You will find a link to this at nav.no/minside (my page).

sendInnKomplett.tittel: The application is ready for submission. Do you want to send it now?
liste: Today's date will be set as the date of receipt of the application.

kvittering.mottattDokumenter: We received the following documents on {{dato}}:
kvittering.maaEttersendes: Documents that must be sent later:
kvittering.sendesAvAndre: Documents to be sent by others:
kvittering.fristEttersending: Deadline for sending the missing documents: {{dato}}
kvittering.ettersendingsInfo: We cannot process your case until we have received all the required documents. The task for sending the remaining documents can be found at nav.no/minside (my page).
kvittering.altMottatInfo: All necessary documents have been received. You can find them under Dine saker (Your cases) at nav.no/minside (my page).

feil.fraBackend: We are experiencing technical difficulties. We apologize for the inconvenience. Please try again later. If the problem persists, you can get help from NAV Service Centre at (+47) 55 55 33 33 or at your local NAV office.

404.tittel: We did not find that page
404.overskrift: We did not find that page
404.p1: The page you requested cannot be found. It may have been deleted, moved, or there may be an error in the link that led you here. We apologize for the inconvenience.
404.p2: We would appreciate it if you report the error via the link below.

500.p1: The page or service is currently unavailable due to a technical error.
